com.gridgraph.driver

Class GridGraphBaseClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.driver.GridGraphBaseClient

  • public class GridGraphBaseClient
extends Object
    A GridGraphBaseClient is a generic Grid Graph client application implmentation to support connecting to a remote GridGraph by using Cluster and @Client, after a property file is provided with detailed remote Grid Graph server information.
    Author:
    guobao.chen
